  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Definicija:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; x_n = ({1248}^n\\bmod 32323) - 16161 \\\\\n&#x26; y_n = ({8421}^n\\bmod 30103) - 15051 \\\\\n&#x26; P_n = \\{(x_1, y_1), (x_2, y_2), \\ldots, (x_n, y_n)\\}\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Na primer,\n$$P_8 = \\{(-14913, -6630), (-10161, 5625), (5226, 11896), (8340, -10778), (15852, -5203), (-15165, 11295), (-1427, -14495), (12407, 1060)\\}$$</p>\n<p>Neka $C(n)$ bude trougaoni broj čije su vrhovi u $P_n$ koji imaju unutrašnje poreklo.</p>\n<p>Primeri:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; C(8) = 20 \\\\\n&#x26; C(600) = 8,950,634 \\\\\n&#x26; C(40,000) = 2,666,610,948,988\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Pronađi $C(2,000,000)$.</p>\n</section>",
